"{\"content\":{\"body\":\"[男孩](https://www.wenzhangba.com/huati/nanhai/)[来自](https://www.wenzhangba.com/writer/laizi/)[江南](https://www.wenzhangba.com/huati/jiangnan/)[小镇](https://www.wenzhangba.com/zhuanti/xiaozhen/)，[女孩](https://www.wenzhangba.com/huati/nvhai/)是[地道](https://www.wenzhangba.com/zhuanti/didao/)的北京女孩，他们[初见](https://www.wenzhangba.com/zhuanti/chujian/)，就如[宝玉](https://www.wenzhangba.com/zhuanti/baoyu_80/)初见[黛玉](https://www.wenzhangba.com/zhuanti/daiyu_5/)：“这个[妹妹](https://www.wenzhangba.com/huati/meimei/)，我是见过的。”\\n\\n　　相恋四年，[毕业](https://www.wenzhangba.com/zhuanti/biye/)的[时候](https://www.wenzhangba.com/zhuanti/shihou/)，女孩把男孩带回[家](https://www.wenzhangba.com/source/jia/)。[母亲](https://www.wenzhangba.com/huati/muqin/)问他的[家世](https://www.wenzhangba.com/zhuanti/jiashi_7/)，男孩一五一十说了。女孩惊觉[自己](https://www.wenzhangba.com/huati/ziji/)的母亲变了[脸色](https://www.wenzhangba.com/zhuanti/lianse/)，然后[拂袖而去](https://www.wenzhangba.com/huati/fuxiuerqu/)，下了逐客令。\\n\\n　　“怎么了？”女[孩心](https://www.wenzhangba.com/zhuanti/haixin/)里[忐忑](https://www.wenzhangba.com/zhuanti/kengdao/)地问母亲。\\n\\n　　母亲说，因为一些[恩怨](https://www.wenzhangba.com/zhuanti/enyuan/)，他[爸爸](https://www.wenzhangba.com/huati/baba/)间接杀死了你爸爸，那时，女孩还小。母亲说：“你能嫁给他吗？你嫁给他，我宁可撞死。”\\n\\n　　男孩[不相信](https://www.wenzhangba.com/huati/xiangxin/)，回到南方[小城](https://www.wenzhangba.com/source/xiaocheng/)，疯了似的去问[父亲](https://www.wenzhangba.com/huati/fuqin/)。父亲[沉默](https://www.wenzhangba.com/huati/chenmo/)很久才说：“那个时候太[乱](https://www.wenzhangba.com/writer/luan/)了，有些事，[说不清](https://www.wenzhangba.com/huati/shuobuqing/)……”之后是[长久](https://www.wenzhangba.com/zhuanti/changjiu/)的沉默。\\n\\n　　02\\n\\n　　刹间[江河](https://www.wenzhangba.com/zhuanti/jianghe/)逆转，一对相恋的人，因为上一辈人的恩怨就要画上[句号](https://www.wenzhangba.com/zhuanti/juhao/)。\\n\\n　　怎能肯[心](https://www.wenzhangba.com/source/xin/)甘？女孩跪在母亲面前，求母亲放[爱](https://www.wenzhangba.com/source/ai/)[一条](https://www.wenzhangba.com/source/yitiao/)[生路](https://www.wenzhangba.com/zhuanti/shenglu/)。母亲说：“除非我死，否则[永远](https://www.wenzhangba.com/huati/yongyuan/)不[可能](https://www.wenzhangba.com/zhuanti/kenen/)。”母亲为她守了20多年寡，她如何[舍得](https://www.wenzhangba.com/source/shede/)这如[血亲](https://www.wenzhangba.com/zhuanti/xueqin/)情？\\n\\n　　女孩[绝望](https://www.wenzhangba.com/huati/juewang/)了，哭着对男孩说[分手](https://www.wenzhangba.com/huati/fenshou/)：“除了你，我一[辈子](https://www.wenzhangba.com/zhuanti/beizi_2/)不嫁。我等你，哪怕，从[青丝](https://www.wenzhangba.com/zhuanti/qingsi/)，到[白头](https://www.wenzhangba.com/zhuanti/baitou/)。”男孩[泪流满面](https://www.wenzhangba.com/huati/leiliumanmian/)地抱着她：“除了你，我谁也不娶，哪怕等到来世。”\\n\\n　　那是在上[世纪](https://www.wenzhangba.com/zhuanti/shiji_5/)80[年代](https://www.wenzhangba.com/zhuanti/niandai/)，那是[爱情誓言](https://www.wenzhangba.com/aiqingwenzhang/)。他们相约，一辈子不分开，永远为[对方](https://www.wenzhangba.com/zhuanti/duifang/)[坚守](https://www.wenzhangba.com/zhuanti/jianshou/)[爱情](https://www.wenzhangba.com/source/aiqing/)。\\n\\n![](https://images.mirror-media.xyz/publication-images/cAVi9gUZrrUYp6nQHxXfX.png?height=344&width=550)\\n\\n\",\"timestamp\":1640853026,\"title\":\"loverangel\"},\"digest\":\"0vAwxtTHN8VFJg3Y6hturgd_Zc6tjvbQsWJDY-a4oXw\",\"authorship\":{\"contributor\":\"0x6eCC324f9f4c952F6D41645ABC03c9900Ed5fE73\",\"signingKey\":\"{\\\"alg\\\":\\\"ES256\\\",\\\"crv\\\":\\\"P-256\\\",\\\"ext\\\":true,\\\"key_ops\\\":[\\\"verify\\\"],\\\"kty\\\":\\\"EC\\\",\\\"x\\\":\\\"MlvP4Eniq2C4UqtRnRQfSZD-jJzbS0sAAMKkdmOixW8\\\",\\\"y\\\":\\\"CBveijxGRUTApIZ2YTgNzNbDM1WAFneDxxufogGM0wA\\\"}\",\"signature\":\"9INvSqL-864NlsW53CUt5Miv6zMj7t66wx8j1T1kETQSfqGhk8AG12Eei_fsvvFbN2iaVwffol79-dwtuXMhbQ\",\"signingKeySignature\":\"0x5ab5e255c16978e3abfccea4a79933a1964204cf52825da7fcece874ad3b7879528da63376e4a9d28f7c080da75d40bf0404197f35757fb739fb4521826131eb1b\",\"signingKeyMessage\":\"I authorize publishing on mirror.xyz from this device using:\\n{\\\"alg\\\":\\\"ES256\\\",\\\"crv\\\":\\\"P-256\\\",\\\"ext\\\":true,\\\"key_ops\\\":[\\\"verify\\\"],\\\"kty\\\":\\\"EC\\\",\\\"x\\\":\\\"MlvP4Eniq2C4UqtRnRQfSZD-jJzbS0sAAMKkdmOixW8\\\",\\\"y\\\":\\\"CBveijxGRUTApIZ2YTgNzNbDM1WAFneDxxufogGM0wA\\\"}\",\"algorithm\":{\"name\":\"ECDSA\",\"hash\":\"SHA-256\"}},\"nft\":{},\"version\":\"12-21-2020\",\"originalDigest\":\"0vAwxtTHN8VFJg3Y6hturgd_Zc6tjvbQsWJDY-a4oXw\"}"